spec_data.Name: texlive-libertinust1math
spec_data.Description:
The package provides a Type1 version of Libertinus Math, with a
number of additions and changes, plus LaTeX support files that
allow it to serve as a math accompaniment to Libertine under
LaTeX.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:29:21 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A Type 1 font and LaTeX support for Libertinus Math
